All staff very pleasant, the guy who checked us in couldn't do enough for us, and we were confident that any query would be efficiently and professionally dealt with, but equally staff were not intrusive and left us alone to enjoy our stay.	The staff at reception are very helpful and friendly and this is great of course, but the poor guys seem to be always short-staffed compared to the great number of customers in front of them.	The staff was really friendly and helpful (including communicating in English); the room was great - spacious, tidy and well furnished.	The staff who were on duty at breakfast were helpful and efficient and the breakfast room was also spotlessly clean.